<ab facs="#facs_224_r1l5">beſandt vnd <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒurede geſacʒt . der meynt wıe Jm von dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan cert="unknown">C .</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_224_r1l6"><expan>ſtey<ex>n</ex>man</expan> vngütlıch <expan>geſchehe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſey / wıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſo hat er vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> daʒ </ab>
